title: Kenya: Nyeri Governor Nderitu Gachagua is dead - The Standard
text:
Your are here » Home » Kenya Nyeri Governor Nderitu Gachagua is dead By Patel Okumu | Updated Fri, February 24th 2017 at 10:05 GMT +3 SHARE THIS ARTICLE Share on Twitter Governor Nderitu Gachagua. 
Nyeri Governor Nderitu Gachagua has dies at aged 64 while receiving treatment at a London hospital, Deputy Governor Samuel Wamathai confirms. 
Nderitu Gachagua served as the MP for Mathira constituency before becoming Governor. 
He has been ailing for a long and was undergoing treatment in London. His absence left residents speculating on his condition and his ability to lead and fend off his political opponents.
